---
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="comments" aria-labelledby="comments-title">
  <h2 id="comments-title">讨论与反馈</h2>
  <p>评论系统预留为 giscus。当前未配置 GitHub Discussions 仓库参数，可先通过 GitHub 或邮箱交流。</p>
  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button" href={site.github}>GitHub</a>
    <a class="button primary" href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>邮箱联系</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .comments {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-top: 42px;
    padding: 22px;
    background: rgb(9 20 36 / 62%);
  }

  h2,
  p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>
